Description

  Lead a team of Warehouse staff to run the daily operations
  Pick, pack and issuance of goods
  Check all received goods to ensure correct quantity and is in good condition
  Perform inventory stock take and monitoring of product shelf life
  Ensure proper housekeeping in warehouse
  Any ad-hoc duties as assigned by Superior

Requirements

  Possess positive attitude and initiative
  Ability to work well as a team
  Possess good communication skills in Mandarin and English – both written and verbal due to the need to communicate and liaise with Chinese-speaking customers
  Proficient in MS Word and MS Excel
